{"tid":101623,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【有乜咁奇】14歲自閉女蘆葦叢內凍傷送院，母7公里外凍死","createTime":"2017-01-31T04:28:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-31T10:26:16.000Z","uid":37661,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7d9d0394a01f39b6b6ccb84d2cf99955c0a19187","tid":101623,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T04:28:17.000Z","msg":"【短片】黑龍江離奇命案　14歲自閉女蘆葦叢內凍傷送院　母7公里外凍死<br />\n<br />\n (00:41) 2017/1/31<br />\n<br />\n內地黑龍江省大慶市日前發生母死女凍傷的離奇命案。一名14歲少女在蘆葦叢雪地中被凍傷獲救，靠社交媒體與其父親取得聯繫後，發現少女的母親事前無故離開住所，其後凍死在相隔約7公里外的一個油井旁。由於少女患自閉證，獲救後一直有未開口說話，案件疑團未解。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170131/s00004/1485794404519SL4_44477A99239D8D7DB60175D6D1436E7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170131%2Fs00004%2F1485794404519SL4_44477A99239D8D7DB60175D6D1436E7C.jpg&h=76398ca8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170131/s00004/1485787279940\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170131%2Fs00004%2F1485787279940&d=rjg6%2Bw4p6Mv2XY9C6AOo56WGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=c0cac72a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170131%2Fs00004%2F1485787279940&h=b7697954\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170131/s00004/1485787279940</a>"},{"pid":"eee39cd2b0049fdf658f94f2464b9d432f7446cb","tid":101623,"uid":16880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T04:31:24.000Z","msg":"自閉症係咪有個自閉證"},{"pid":"9bd53e33ea864abce6e629a22be747d22cf8033a","tid":101623,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T04:31:34.000Z","msg":"爛果報道<br />\n<br />\n乜撚嘢中文嚟架～～<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n上周四年廿九，<span style=\"color: red;\">黑龍大慶</span>發生一宗離奇命案。當日有民眾於一蘆葦叢中，發現一女孩被凍得奄奄一息。<span style=\"color: red;\">女孩被送往身子蜷縮成一團</span>，手腳凍得似木板，呈凍僵狀態。而最離奇的是，女孩母親於六、七公里凍死，箇中原因不明。<br />\n<br />\n女孩父親表示，前一天上午，妻子要他外出為電話服務增值，然而事後回家，兩母女卻不知所蹤。女孩一直不肯開口說話，事件還在調查中。<br />\n<br />\n梨視頻  <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170131/56240920\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170131%2F56240920&d=rjg6%2Bw4p6Mv2XY9C6AOo56WGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=b7e60ddd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170131%2F56240920&h=2349378f\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170131/56240920</a>"},{"pid":"104de2fd14ef129e63db9af598b0e2f4e4f67550","tid":101623,"uid":34714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T04:34:42.000Z","msg":"個女做 係boss黎 大奸角"},{"pid":"bb81a370ed2009314b744e4ff6af4b93ec29fb16","tid":101623,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T04:47:11.000Z","msg":"個老母搵女結果..."},{"pid":"e08b390ff97aef3bb6c22e4f333632cb6ac1cb41","tid":101623,"uid":36287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T06:34:54.000Z","msg":"自閉證係咩黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8794cfdd9b0e37d13fdb255a36afa4dcaee1b35c","tid":101623,"uid":70689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T06:51:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自閉證係咩黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/yeu8ftq9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fyeu8ftq9&h=9b1f27ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n搵唔到高清版<br />\ngoogle cap圖"},{"pid":"7ada211db23ff8e44dd3a1cfd241b79efc415ccd","tid":101623,"uid":4575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T09:22:13.000Z","msg":"u 竟然是個boy"},{"pid":"fe3d60275d8353a55933f505edb80296807d0c11","tid":101623,"uid":41821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-0